#######################################################################################

This script assumes that you already have sudo configured for the user wich executes it

Please, download wordpress.sh to your machine and make it executable 
Do sh wordpress.sh 

Login to your WordPress server by your browser with user nuvym and password nuvym
Don't forget to change this password! 


